      <title>荷兰银行收购复星德国银行进军财富管理领域</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/abn-amro-buys-german-bank-hauck-aufhauser-from-china-s-fosun</link>
      <description><![CDATA[荷兰银行 (ABN Amro Bank NV) 同意以 6.72 亿欧元（7.3 亿美元）收购德国银行 Hauck &amp; Aufhäuser Lampe Privatbank AG，扩大这家荷兰公司在财富管理领域的影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/abn-amro-buys-german-bank-hauck-aufhauser-from-china-s-fosun</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
