      <title>欧佩克+会议前地缘政治紧张局势加剧，油价稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-may-28</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管中东紧张局势因一名埃及士兵在与以色列军队的冲突中死亡而加剧，但油价在连续两天上涨后企稳。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-may-28</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 23:28:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据说 Vedanta 将于 6 月考虑出售 10 亿美元的股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/vedanta-is-said-to-weigh-1-billion-share-sale-as-soon-as-june</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，印度大宗商品大亨阿尼尔·阿加瓦尔 (Anil Agarwal) 旗下的韦丹塔有限公司 (Vedanta Ltd.) 正在考虑最快在未来几周内出售股票，这可能筹集高达 850 亿卢比（10 亿美元）的资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/vedanta-is-said-to-weigh-1-billion-share-sale-as-soon-as-june</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 11:01:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿达尼旗舰能源公司获得董事会批准筹集 35 亿美元资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/adani-flagship-energy-unit-seek-board-nod-to-raise-2-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁高塔姆·阿达尼 (Gautam Adani) 帝国的旗舰公司阿达尼企业有限公司 (Adani Enterprises Ltd.) 已获得董事会批准，将筹集高达 1660 亿卢比（20 亿美元）的资金，而一天前，该集团的电力公用事业部门也获得了类似的 15 亿美元融资批准。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/adani-flagship-energy-unit-seek-board-nod-to-raise-2-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 10:31:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
